return (double) (getSampleSize() * getNumberOfSuccesses()) / (double) getPopulationSize();
{code}
it could do:
{code}
return getSampleSize() * ((double) getNumberOfSuccesses() / (double) getPopulationSize());
{code}
This seemed to fix it, based on a quick test.

